WEBVTT

1
00:48:11.680 --> 00:48:16.196 
我找出毛病来了 这表里面的轮子太多了
I see what's wrong with this. Why, this watch is full of wheels.

2
00:48:16.280 --> 00:48:19.795 
我可怜的表 我可怜的轮子和弹簧
Oh, my poor watch. Oh, my wheels and springs.

3
00:48:20.840 --> 00:48:23.195 
可是… 黄油 当然
- But, but, but, but, but, but, but, but-- - Butter! Of course!

4
00:48:23.280 --> 00:48:25.874 
我需要点儿黄油 黄油！
It needs some butter. Butter!

5
00:48:25.960 --> 00:48:29.032 
黄油！ 黄油？
- Butter! - But-but-butter?

6
00:48:29.120 --> 00:48:32.749 
黄油 哦 谢谢你 黄油 是的 好了
Butter. Oh, thank you. Butter. Yes, that's fine.

7
00:48:32.840 --> 00:48:35.229 
哦 不 不 你会把碎屑弄进去的
Oh, no, no! No, no, no! You'll get crumbs in it.

8
00:48:35.320 --> 00:48:38.232 
这是最好的黄油 你在说什么？
Oh, this is the very best butter. What are you talking about?

9
00:48:38.320 --> 00:48:40.788 
茶？ 茶？我没想到要茶
- Tea? - Tea! Oh, I never thought of tea! Of course.

10
00:48:40.880 --> 00:48:43.348 
当然茶 不 不！不要茶！
- Don't! Don't! Not tea! - Tea.

11
00:48:43.480 --> 00:48:46.438 
糖？ 糖 两勺 只要两勺
- Sugar? -Sugar? Two spoons. Yes, y-- Two spoons.

